<headline>Special Weather Statement issued November 27 at 4:17PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Snow Behind Snow Squall Will Decrease Over the Next Hour...
Snow behind a snow squall that passed through the Helena region
will generally decrease in intensity over the next hour. Hazardous
driving conditions may persist longer where snow accumulated on
roadways.</description>
